# D5 recursive-negate: negate on a recursive SCC over a @differential
# negated view. src=1, chain 1->2->3->4.
#
# Batch 1: seed the chain and the source. reach = {1,2,3,4}.
# Batch 2: +dead 3. Kills reach(3) and (transitively) reach(4). reach = {1,2}.
# Batch 3: -dead 3. Restores reach(3) and reach(4). reach = {1,2,3,4}.
# Batch 4: same-batch flap +dead 3 / -dead 3 (nets zero). reach = {1,2,3,4}.
batch
+ src 1
+ edge 1 2
+ edge 2 3
+ edge 3 4
end

batch
+ dead 3
end

batch
- dead 3
end

batch
+ dead 3
- dead 3
end
